{
  "id": "613354f12af24a0022872a6e",
  "title": "HTML は TeX を置き換えられるか",
  "created": 1630754035,
  "updated": 1733337104,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "613354f12af24a0022872a6e",
      "text": "HTML は TeX を置き換えられるか",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754035,
      "updated": 1630754643
    },
    {
      "id": "6133555bd1a02f0000948586",
      "text": "[HTML]/[CSS] で論文フォーマット、意外と作れるかもしれない？[hata6502.icon]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754140,
      "updated": 1630754233
    },
    {
      "id": "6133555bd1a02f0000948587",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754140,
      "updated": 1630754140
    },
    {
      "id": "61335542d1a02f0000948585",
      "text": "\tCSS で[2段組み]を作れる。",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1630754115,
      "updated": 1733337104
    },
    {
      "id": "61335540d1a02f0000948583",
      "text": "　　https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Columns/Using_multi-column_layouts",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754113,
      "updated": 1630754127
    },
    {
      "id": "61336d958ee92a000036a208",
      "text": "　　これが一番大事な気がしますね [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630760341,
      "updated": 1630760363
    },
    {
      "id": "61335541d1a02f0000948584",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754113,
      "updated": 1630754113
    },
    {
      "id": "613354f2d1a02f000094857b",
      "text": "\tページネーションが気になる。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754035,
      "updated": 1630754205
    },
    {
      "id": "61335507d1a02f000094857c",
      "text": "　\t印刷時にページ番号をふったりするのが難しそう。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754055,
      "updated": 1630754132
    },
    {
      "id": "675014ca71b3c20000bccaa7",
      "text": "  　ブラウザの印刷機能側でページ番号を振ってくれます[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1733301469,
      "updated": 1733301469
    },
    {
      "id": "61335507d1a02f000094857d",
      "text": "　\t\t出来るかもしれない!?[hata6502.icon]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754055,
      "updated": 1630754132
    },
    {
      "id": "61335507d1a02f000094857e",
      "text": " 　\t[https://triple-underscore.github.io/css-page-ja.html CSS Paged Media Module Level 3 （日本語訳）]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754055,
      "updated": 1630754132
    },
    {
      "id": "61336d838ee92a000036a207",
      "text": " 　それは絶対重要というほどでもないと思う [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630760323,
      "updated": 1630760337
    },
    {
      "id": "613355a1d1a02f0000948588",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754209,
      "updated": 1630754209
    },
    {
      "id": "61335507d1a02f000094857f",
      "text": "\t[TeX] は画像をいい感じの場所に挿入してくれて便利ですね。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754055,
      "updated": 1630754224
    },
    {
      "id": "613355a4d1a02f0000948589",
      "text": "\t\tHTML だとどうすればいいのだろう。[hata6502.icon]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754213,
      "updated": 1630754215
    },
    {
      "id": "61335507d1a02f0000948580",
      "text": "  TeXの画像の場所指定は大変なのでHTMLみたいなのでOKだと思います [増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "566fa156776c9b11008ee92a",
      "created": 1630754055,
      "updated": 1630760309
    },
    {
      "id": "6133562dd1a02f000094858d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754350,
      "updated": 1630754350
    },
    {
      "id": "613355e8d1a02f000094858b",
      "text": "技術的に可能であっても、HTML が TeX を置き換えるためには[説得]が必要そう。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754281,
      "updated": 1630754363
    },
    {
      "id": "613355f1d1a02f000094858c",
      "text": "\tTeX と Word は [de facto standard]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754290,
      "updated": 1630754499
    },
    {
      "id": "613356b0d1a02f000094858e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1630754481,
      "updated": 1630754481
    },
    {
      "id": "61426b7a1280f00000be00a5",
      "text": "既にHTMLで[組版]するprojectが立ち上がっていた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1631742842,
      "updated": 1631746851
    },
    {
      "id": "61426b8b1280f00000be00a7",
      "text": " [Vivliostyle]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1631742860,
      "updated": 1631742861
    },
    {
      "id": "61426b7b1280f00000be00a6",
      "text": " [Twight]もそれっぽい[blu3mo.icon]",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1631742844,
      "updated": 1646747117
    },
    {
      "id": "6142946f79e1130000e54c16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d89b1f60230ae001779e113",
      "created": 1631753327,
      "updated": 1631753327
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbafa4bb2e20000707de1",
      "text": "個人的にHTMLが台頭するのであれば[脱組版]の流れで来てほしさがある[kuuote.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1640872697,
      "updated": 1733337059
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbafd4bb2e20000707de2",
      "text": " 美しい論文を組み立てるのは本質ではないと思う",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1640872701,
      "updated": 1640872755
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbb4c4bb2e20000707de5",
      "text": "  読みたいフォーマットで読める方が大事",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1640872781,
      "updated": 1640872795
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbc784bb2e2000008e105",
      "text": "   例えば[Zenn]がまとまった記事の塊を「本」と呼んでいるのはいいなと思う",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1640873026,
      "updated": 1640873054
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbb344bb2e20000707de4",
      "text": " [kuuote.icon]はアカデミアの人間ではないので勝手な感想ですが",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
      "created": 1640872756,
      "updated": 1640872770
    },
    {
      "id": "61cdbb244bb2e20000707de3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5e8944948a182900174bb2e2",
